Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.24,0:00:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来…并不是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.04,0:00:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂浮在小镇上的飞碟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.19,0:00:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在我们身边的诺艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.97,0:00:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.58,0:00:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.59,0:00:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.12,0:00:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.92,0:00:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都忘了诺艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.98,0:00:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我却什么也做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.40,0:00:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  幸好汐音还记得
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.69,0:00:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是让我知道自己不是孤独的也好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.77,0:00:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.27,0:00:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所了解的乃乃香这个女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.08,0:00:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦决定了什么  就绝对要做到最后不罢休
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.73,0:01:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既率直又坦诚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.68,0:01:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话语之中带着能激励大家的魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.36,0:01:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.93,0:01:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所认识的朋友  应该是一个这样的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.28,0:01:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.48,0:01:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  汐音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.34,0:01:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.82,0:01:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是被永不放弃的乃乃香激励起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.50,0:01:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请相信我说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.51,0:01:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.70,0:01:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能听我说我的愿望吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.59,0:01:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  当然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.69,0:02:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想再一次  把大家集合在天文台
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.23,0:02:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTA-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.71,0:03:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.57,0:03:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:03:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.94,0:04:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  我正在找你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.81,0:04:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.21,0:04:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.50,0:04:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望小春也能来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.43,0:04:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来不止乃乃香  就连汐音也回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.56,0:04:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这倒不是  只是我的学校在放暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.31,0:04:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅游啊  白期待了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.51,0:04:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还想着大家又能够在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.59,0:04:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.01,0:04:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连汐音也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.48,0:05:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次打算做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.04,0:05:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家再在天文台集合一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.20,0:05:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像那个时候一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.20,0:05:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确那个时候我们按照乃乃香所说的呼唤了飞碟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.88,0:05:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是飞碟没有来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.68,0:05:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔什么的  我根本不认识
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凑太
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.41,0:05:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不认识诺艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.81,0:05:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不认识  可是却一直放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.45,0:05:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.29,0:05:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香说过的话  在脑中挥之不去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在寻找关于这个素不相识的女孩的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.26,0:05:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不可能找得到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.79,0:05:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却一直找  一直找
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.66,0:05:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.55,0:05:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.96,0:05:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.78,0:05:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.87,0:06:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白的  好像有什么东西浮现在脑袋里一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.95,0:06:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春  凑太也是这样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.00,0:06:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.29,0:06:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明知道失去了些什么很重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.70,0:06:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是却想不起来那是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.05,0:06:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.29,0:06:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我放心了  原来大家都是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.17,0:06:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季也是  小春也是  凑太也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.31,0:06:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是  乃乃香也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.93,0:06:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一定被同样的回忆联系在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.69,0:06:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从七年前那个时候开始
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.90,0:06:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.46,0:06:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须再次确认一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.90,0:06:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在重要的东西就要从我们之间消失得无影无踪之前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.97,0:07:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.98,0:07:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起来呼唤飞碟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.59,0:07:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.75,0:07:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前没这么破烂的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.63,0:07:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.96,0:07:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候在这里度过的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.07,0:07:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今往后也一直不变
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.38,0:07:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔最喜欢我们的笑容了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.23,0:07:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.58,0:07:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总感觉好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.57,0:08:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.38,0:08:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.79,0:08:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季明明能够平静地在大家面前做些大胆的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.11,0:08:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.65,0:08:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想见识一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.42,0:08:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外一个柚季做了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.13,0:08:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想见诺艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.61,0:08:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.42,0:08:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想见诺艾尔妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.27,0:08:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟诺艾尔再一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.19,0:08:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔  能听见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.76,0:08:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家说想见你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.16,0:08:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我们大家共同的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.88,0:08:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.91,0:09:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音的帽子
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.75,0:10:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易才见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.99,0:10:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还会在这待上一阵子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.50,0:10:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住的地方呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.59,0:10:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.67,0:10:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  住在我家了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.11,0:10:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.42,0:10:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.96,0:10:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抽空来我店里玩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.64,0:10:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.51,0:10:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.50,0:10:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸的话  没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.83,0:10:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那时也没介意诺艾尔住我家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.01,0:10:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.44,0:11:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟妈妈约定好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.97,0:11:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后乃乃香要体验很多东西  不断成长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.70,0:11:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成长过程中可能会遇到悲伤的事情  难过的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.93,0:11:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是在那个时候  正因为是那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.75,0:11:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要竭尽全力用微笑去迎接它
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.39,0:11:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话  无论是什么困难都会迎刃而解的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.25,0:11:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么困难都可以？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.95,0:11:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.17,0:12:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香的话一定可以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.98,0:12:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  约好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.61,0:12:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.50,0:12:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.15,0:12:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候  我在这里碰到一个独自一人坐着的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.78,0:12:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候我在想  一定要和这个女孩成为朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.46,0:12:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不能成为朋友的话  会后悔一辈子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.99,0:12:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.30,0:12:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能与你相遇  真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.51,0:12:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.24,0:14:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.86,0:14:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.59,0:14:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  总算醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.30,0:14:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.43,0:14:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有点事情  去北美市了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.50,0:14:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.56,0:14:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  弄好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.06,0:14:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋包饭？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.16,0:14:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  人家叫我弄的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.20,0:14:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.23,0:14:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  叫啥来着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.48,0:15:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  刚才还在那的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.12,0:15:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐在妈妈的椅子上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.16,0:15:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.02,0:15:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.33,0:15:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.78,0:15:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.46,0:15:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果只有我记得诺艾尔了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.48,0:15:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果连我也忘记了诺艾尔的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.19,0:15:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她或许真的就消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.64,0:15:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.83,0:15:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要留下所有…我关于诺艾尔的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.89,0:16:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要一直做好朋友哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.17,0:16:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.85,0:17:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.66,0:17:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.79,0:17:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  凑太
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.84,0:17:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下  无视我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.23,0:17:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不如「反对」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.70,0:17:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  哥哥你个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.70,0:17:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我帮忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.81,0:17:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就会好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.25,0:17:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是男孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.86,0:17:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.78,0:18:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪兽先生会一直精精神神的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.72,0:18:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.35,0:18:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凑太
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.15,0:18:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.98,0:18:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.58,0:18:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.16,0:18:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须要去找你的朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.17,0:18:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有很多很多话想和你说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.40,0:18:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有许许多多的珍贵回忆想要保留下来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.08,0:18:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔  我想见你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.08,0:19:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会见到的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.65,0:22:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.34,0:22:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.93,0:22:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来  诺艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.08,0:23:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
